---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Fund Investigator"
  description="Privacy Policy for Fund Investigator"
>
  <section class="pt-40 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-navy mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-8">

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Last updated: January 2, 2026
        </p>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>
            Fund Investigator collects minimal information necessary to provide our service. This includes usage data such as pages visited and features accessed to improve the user experience.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">2. How We Use Information</h2>
          <p>
            Information collected is used solely to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Provide and improve our analytical tools and services</li>
            <li>Understand usage patterns to enhance user experience</li>
            <li>Respond to user inquiries and support requests</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">3. Data Sources</h2>
          <p>
            All mutual fund data displayed on Fund Investigator is sourced from publicly available AMFI (Association of Mutual Funds in India) data. We do not collect or store personal financial information.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
          <p>
            We use Cloudflare Web Analytics, a privacy-friendly analytics service that does not use cookies or collect personal information. This service tracks anonymous pageviews and basic usage statistics to help us improve the website. We also use Cloudflare Browser Errors to detect and fix technical issues. Neither service identifies individual users or tracks behavior across websites.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">5. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell, trade, or rent user information to third parties. We do not share personal information except as required by law.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">6. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement reasonable security measures to protect information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">7. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">8. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@fundinvestigator.com" class="text-navy hover:text-gold font-medium">contact@fundinvestigator.com</a>
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
